data.description: Welcome to Paradise! This lovely 2 bedroom, 2 bath home has it all. New ROOF, New A/C, New vinyl flooring throughout, interior and exterior professionally painted. Large living room in addition to a large florida room with views of the park located directly across the street. Lovely dining room with built-in cabinets. Both bedrooms have walk in closets. Interior laundry room with storage and folding table. Large outside storage room, screened patio in carport.  Room sizes appx. & subject to error.
